Note:  This summary of the Canadian Gas Potential Committee Report outlines
the basic downside analysis of the reserves that exist in the Alaskan Front=
ier
as well as the coalbed methane gas.  There will much discussion on this top=
ic
over the next few months.  Anyone that wants a copy of the entire Canadian
